tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE sustainable_packaging_practices (
  supplier_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  supplier_name TEXT,
  packaging_type TEXT,
  packaging_material TEXT,
  sustainability_rating FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE sustainable_packaging_practices (
    supplier_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_name VARCHAR(255),
    packaging_material VARCHAR(255),
    packaging_type VARCHAR(50),
    packaging_recyclable BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE packaging_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    analysis_result VARCHAR(100)
    FOREIGN KEY (supplier_id) REFERENCES sustainable_packaging_practices(supplier_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Products ( 
 product_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
 product_name TEXT, 
 supplier_id INT, 
 packaging_material TEXT, 
 FOREIGN KEY (supplier_id) REFERENCES Suppliers(supplier_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE Orders ( 
 order_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
 product_id INT, 
 order_date DATE, 
 quantity INT, 
 FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES Products(product_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE suppliers (
    supplier_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_name TEXT,
    packaging_material TEXT,
    sustainable_practices BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    supplier_id INT,
    packaging_type TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE sales (
    sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    sale_date DATE,
    quantity INT,
    total_price DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE analyses (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    result TEXT
)
